snippet.title: Trepang2 Survival Mode DLC
snippet.description:
New combat simulator mode. Fight 50 randomised waves of enemies across 10 maps, complete objectives and eat food to survive. Waves, maps and objectives are randomized so it plays different every time.

FEATURES:

- Combat Simulator Survival Mode
- 10 weapon skins
- Jiggly Boi player outfit
- 3 grenades: vortex grenade, thruster grenade, decoy grenade
- 2 cheats: 
Hunted: Assassins will spawn when you least expect it...
Loyal Follower: A friendly invincible cultist will follow you

Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/trepang2/9ncdmpcpdtqf
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10007968

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1164940/Trepang2/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/trepang2

Twitter: https://twitter.com/TrepangStudios
Discord: https://trepang2.com/discord
https://www.trepang2game.com/
